Package pl.polsl.mostowska.integrationwebapp.model

package pl.polsl.mostowska.integrationwebapp.model
The model package encapsulates the core computational logic of the application, responsible for performing mathematical operations, such as numerical integration. It is designed to be independent of user interaction and solely focuses on the computation layer of the application. This package serves as the foundation for the application's mathematical computations and is designed to work seamlessly with other application layers, such as the user interface or data input/output mechanisms.
